node.text:
#Ad I used to think I could get away with anything — until Google Nest sent my humans the new #NestCam and #NestDoorbell. Now they get alerts when I make mischief. Speaking of which, they just went to the grocery store. What better time to show them my new countertops parkour routine. 😈

I want to see what all my pet friends get into when their humans are away. Share your own Nest Cam pet videos with #CaughtOnNestCam for a chance to be featured on @madebygoogle
